snippet.title: Top 10 Reasons Amber Heard Was Cancelled
snippet.description:
Top 10 Reasons Amber Heard Was Cancelled

Join us in today’s video as we show you Top 10 Reasons Amber Heard Was Cancelled. Amber Heard, who plays Mera in the Aquaman series, has allegedly violated a clause in her contract. For the past few months, a petition has been circulating (receiving nearly two million signatures) calling for Amber Heard to be fired from DC Comics film adaptations.

She and the Pirates of the Caribbean star were divorced in 2017. Before the divorce was finalised, the actress filed for a restraining order against him, presenting photos that “captured the mark on her face as she walked in and out of a Los Angeles court” as evidence. Be sure to watch the whole video for the full details about this and in addition, do us a favor and like the video and subscribe and turn on the notification bell. We’ll see you in the next video!
